98dca6e2f","tid":1667942,"uid":35341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a8aeece82695d4767acc20ed34ef32efdcd9497","tid":1667942,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"Ching 咁搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"是其是 非其非"},{"pid":"b9f15ab504071ff9be075050f156bdc71f050c01","tid":1667942,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"2987d627f05d7359677a972ab6bbbb39c8ee9527","tid":1667942,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1c1ffdd9a8012c54ab9b34c02a7290eee05de9","tid":1667942,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:11:21